snippet.title: NAVY SEALS: covert operations Trailer
snippet.description: This is the trailer video for the Quake 3 tactical shooter mod NS:CO (www.ns-co.net) developed by Team Mirage (www.team-mirage.net). Music from MattMRE, Trailer by Beren (www.beren.net) of Renegade Gods (www.renegadegods.com).
